| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1488 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aa7557ec-1e44-5b8e-a626-ab3e9c70f6ce"
